
## Deploy (Streamlit Community Cloud)
- Push this repo to **public** GitHub.
- Go to https://share.streamlit.io → New app → select repo + `app.py`.
- In **Settings → Access**, set **Public**. Test the URL in an incognito window.

## Files
- `app.py` — Streamlit app
- `bias_rules.csv` — editable lexicon (no code change needed to expand)
- `requirements.txt`
- `sample_reviews.csv` (optional demo data)

## Privacy
- No names; only anonymized IDs
- Aggregation gate: n ≥ 5
- Session-only storage; export downloads for audits

## Notes
- Flags are coaching signals, not final judgments.
- AIR (rule-of-thumb ≥ 0.80) is a proxy; human review required.
